title: [Spitfire Alley, Gunner's Lane]
description: The Crow's Nest pub stands shakily on the north side of the street, its clapboard walls peeling paint and desperately in need of a good cleaning.  Whenever the doors to the place swing open, loud sea chanties tumble out, usually followed by a flying body or two and an emphatic "And don't come back neither, ya lubbers!"
